---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Content & Removal — Foot Morning America" description="How to request removal of a listing or report infringing or non-consensual content on Foot Morning America.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl py-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl">Content &amp; Removal Policy</h1>
    <div class="article-body mt-6">
      <p>Foot Morning America hosts no adult content. We operate a directory and news brand that links
        to content created and hosted by third parties, who are solely responsible for it.</p>
      <h2>Requesting removal of a listing</h2>
      <p>If you are a creator (or their authorized representative) and want your listing removed, email
        <span class="dateline">legal@footmorningamerica.com</span> with the listing name and link. We
        remove verified requests promptly.</p>
      <h2>Copyright (DMCA)</h2>
      <p>To report content you believe infringes your copyright, send a notice to
        <span class="dateline">legal@footmorningamerica.com</span> including: identification of the work,
        the URL on our site, your contact information, a good-faith statement, and your signature
        (physical or electronic). We respond to valid notices and remove or disable the material.</p>
      <h2>Non-consensual or underage content</h2>
      <p>We have zero tolerance for non-consensual content or any depiction of a minor. Report it
        immediately to <span class="dateline">legal@footmorningamerica.com</span> and we will remove the
        listing and cooperate with appropriate authorities.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
